headline: Analyst Continues to Back Autodesk (ADSK) Amid Consistent Growth Momentum
summary: Autodesk Inc. (NASDAQ:ADSK) is among the best stocks you’ll wish you bought sooner. On November 28, Taylor McGinnis, an analyst at UBS, lifted the price target on Autodesk from $385 to $400 while maintaining a Buy rating. headline: Autodesk (ADSK) Reports Better-Than-Expected Earnings and Guidance Increase According to Baird
summary: Autodesk Inc. (NASDAQ:ADSK) is one of the most profitable tech stocks to buy. On November 26, Baird raised the firm’s price target on Autodesk to $377 from $367 and maintained an Outperform rating on the shares.
